query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 0
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('copy',
'drag-and-drop',
'elasticsearch',
'javascript-events',
'model-view-controller',
'mysql-workbench',
'nhibernate',
'query-optimization',
'select',
'session',
'swift3',
'themes',
'tkinter');
